ActFarm Income Protection Act
SubjectAgri-Recovery - Agricultural producers in Nova Scotia
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to provide contributions under the Agricultural Disaster Relief Program to assist producers in Nova Scotia in dealing with the impacts of a strawberry virus complex.
